stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Off : wanted = IDLE
    [*] --> Coast : wanted = COASTING

    [*] --> SpinningUp : wanted = SHOOTING

    SpinningUp --> AtSetpoint : velocity within tolerance [debounced]
    AtSetpoint --> Recovering : ball fired [velocity dip past debounce]
    Recovering --> AtSetpoint : velocity recovered to tolerance
    Recovering --> UnderShooting : sustained RPM drop [0.4s debounce]
    UnderShooting --> SpinningUp : wanted state re-entered

    note right of SpinningUp
        Duty-cycle bang-bang.
        Max acceleration.
    end note

    note right of AtSetpoint
        Torque-current bang-bang.
        Consistent hold.
    end note

    note right of Recovering
        Duty-cycle bang-bang.
        Re-spinning after ball pass.
        Launch count incremented.
    end note

    note right of UnderShooting
        Too many rapid shots.
        Flywheel cannot recover.
        Signals shooter to revert.
    end note
